Description: Comprehensive simulation study comparing Trim and Fill, PET-PEESE,
    and Copas selection model for correcting publication bias in meta-analysis.
    Evaluates performance across 135 scenarios varying effect size, heterogeneity,
    study count, and bias mechanism.
